	(45,'Landmarks - Upper Elementary.pdf','Landmarks - Upper Elementary','','','Students differentiate between natural and man-made landmarks. Students investigate  landmarks in their community, state, country and create a visitor’s brochure to share information about their chosen landmark.',2606,4,'2019-03-29 16:44:06','2015-08-01 13:59:36',251344,'jennybuccos'),
	(46,'The Sugar Crystal Experiment - Upper Elementary.pdf','The Sugar Crystal Experiment - Upper Elementary','','','Students explorer the history of sugar cane in Mauritius, then experiment with sugar and water solutions, evaporation, and sugar crystal formation.  ',5055,4,'2019-06-05 12:05:38','2017-01-01 15:59:52',236077,'jennybuccos'),
